{"word":"G878 - ἄφρων - áphrōn - af'-rone - Fool","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄφρων</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">áphrōn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">af'-rone</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fool</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மதிகேடான, பேதை, புத்தியீன, புத்தியில்லாத, மதியற்ற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"without reason, senseless, foolish, stupid; without refection or intelligence, acting rashly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G5424 - φρήν - phrḗn - frane/5424\">G5424</a>; properly <i>mindless</i>, that is, <i>stupid</i>, (by implication) <i>ignorant</i>, (specifically) <i>egotistic</i>, (practically) <i>rash</i>, or (morally) <i>unbelieving:</i> - fool (-ish), unwise.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5424/5424\">G5424</a>, <a href=\"#/G5426/5426\">G5426</a>, <a href=\"#/G5427/5427\">G5427</a>, <a href=\"#/G5428/5428\">G5428</a>, <a href=\"#/G5429/5429\">G5429</a>, <a href=\"#/G5430/5430\">G5430</a>, <a href=\"#/G877/877\">G877</a>, <a href=\"#/G878/878\">G878</a>"}]}